Ariel's in love.

332
00:28:22,208 --> 00:28:26,421
Ariel? In love?

333
00:28:26,504 --> 00:28:29,132
OK. So far, so good.

334
00:28:29,174 --> 00:28:32,344
I don't think the king knows.

335
00:28:32,428 --> 00:28:37,057
