- ♪ Under the sea ♪
- ♪ Under the sea ♪

392
00:31:44,231 --> 00:31:46,277
♪ When the sardine begin the beguine ♪

393
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:48,237
- ♪ It's music to me ♪
